&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;\end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;table&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tips: include &lt;code&gt;\usepackage{graphicx}&lt;/code&gt; and store images in a &lt;code&gt;figs/&lt;/code&gt; folder. For tables, use &lt;code&gt;booktabs&lt;/code&gt; and avoid â€œgridsâ€ with too many vertical lines.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
